packets.name: PIXLwear P1 Sneaker “The Loft” limited special edition (multicolored), left
packets.author: Pixls
packets.description: In a collaboration between TheCryptoWoman and Pixls.eth, a special PIXLwear P1 sneaker edition called “The Loft” was created. The sneakers perfectly match TheCryptoWoman’s “Skirt - Multicolored” (wearable 2567). The PIXLwear P1 sneaker is a Cryptovoxels shoe for every situation. The P1 model rocks the PIXLwear colours for the tie-free laces and the PIXL P1 stamp on the sole. The insoles are also stamped with “P” and “1” on the left and right shoe, respectively. This is the left shoe. Design: Pixls.eth with TheCryptoWoman. Manufactured with MagicaVoxel. PIXLwear: a PIXL brand - ethical blockchain fashion from Austria.
